description: Average Sans has the color, structure and proportions of its serif sister family, Average, which it complements harmoniously. The neutrality of the forms create a nice texture, both for texts and short headlines. Use it for online magazines, academic texts and blogs. To contribute to the project contact Eduardo Tunni.
